ンが", "４！"]}, {"box": [53, 103, 90, 639], "vertical": true, "font_size": 37, "lines_coords": [[[53.0, 103.0], [90.0, 103.0], [90.0, 639.0], [53.0, 639.0]]], "lines": ["１０ｂｈｏｎｇｒａｍバードウィーク"]}, {"box": [204, 573, 278, 693], "vertical": true, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[243.0, 575.0], [278.0, 575.0], [278.0, 693.0], [243.0, 693.0]], [[204.0, 573.0], [240.0, 573.0], [240.0, 639.0], [204.0, 639.0]]], "lines": ["ニサンが", "６！"]}, {"box": [870, 826, 948, 923], "vertical": true, "font_size": 42, "lines_coords": [[[903.0, 826.0], [948.0, 826.0], [948.0, 923.0], [903.0, 923.0]], [[870.0, 828.0], [908.0, 828.0], [908.0, 895.0], [870.0, 895.0]]], "lines": ["ニシが", "８！！"]}, {"box": [478, 925, 511, 1043], "vertical": true, "font_size": 33, "lines_coords": [[[478.0, 925.0], [511.0, 925.0], [511.0, 1043.0], [478.0, 1043.0]]], "lines": ["ニゴ１０！！"]}, {"box": [243, 856, 400, 1060], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[370.0, 856.0], [396.0, 856.0], [400.0, 959.0], [373.0, 959.0]], [[340.0, 856.0], [367.0, 856.0], [368.0, 1057.0], [342.0, 1057.0]], [[306.0, 856.0], [334.0, 856.0], [337.0, 1060.0], [309.0, 1060.0]], [[275.0, 857.0], [303.0, 857.0], [306.0, 1034.0], [278.0, 1034.0]], [[243.0, 857.0], [270.0, 857.0], [275.0, 1043.0], [248.0, 1043.0]]], "lines": ["先月まて", "「天才を育てる」を", "うたい文句にした", "ｘメｘｘな塾に", "通わされていた。"]}, {"box": [123, 1131, 340, 1360], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[317.0, 1134.0], [339.0, 1134.0], [339.0, 1307.0], [317.0, 1307.0]], [[284.0, 1132.0], [311.0, 1132.0], [309.0, 1310.0], [282.0, 1310.0]], [[248.0, 1132.0], [281.0, 1132.0], [281.0, 1237.0], [248.0, 1237.0]], [[220.0, 1134.0], [246.0, 1134.0], [246.0, 1293.0], [220.0, 1293.0]], [[187.0, 1132.0], [214.0, 1132.0], [214.0, 1285.0], [187.0, 1285.0]], [[156.0, 1132.0], [182.0, 1132.0], [182.0, 1309.0], [156.0, 1309.0]], [[125.0, 1131.0], [151.0, 1131.0], [150.0, 1359.0], [123.0, 1359.0]]], "lines": ["速読をさせたり", "１００ケタの数字を", "１分間で", "暗記させたり、", "そんなことを", "意味もわからず", "やっていた僕は．．．"]}], "img_path": "subarashii_sekai_02_005.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.7", "img_width": 1119, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [534, 126, 602, 382], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[570.0, 128.0], [601.0, 128.0], [601.0, 307.0], [570.0, 307.0]], [[536.0, 126.0], [564.0, 126.0], [562.0, 375.0], [534.0, 375.0]]], "lines": ["ただの天才に", "なってしまったよ。"]}, {"box": [915, 685, 956, 759], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[915.0, 685.0], [956.0, 685.0], [956.0, 759.0], [915.0, 759.0]]], "lines": ["おい。"]}, {"box": [290, 459, 779, 489], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[290.0, 460.0], [779.0, 459.0], [779.0, 487.0], [290.0, 489.0]]], "lines": ["１０ｔｈ．ｐｒｏｇｒａｍバードウィー"]}, {"box": [890, 834, 986, 967], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[951.0, 835.0], [986.0, 835.0], [986.0, 917.0], [951.0, 917.0]], [[926.0, 839.0], [948.0, 839.0], [948.0, 967.0], [926.0, 967.0]], [[890.0, 834.0], [917.0, 834.0], [917.0, 942.0], [890.0, 942.0]]], "lines": ["新しい", "塾の調子は", "どうだ？"]}, {"box": [490, 1081, 613, 1268], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[586.0, 1081.0], [612.0, 1081.0], [612.0, 1232.0], [586.0, 1232.0]], [[553.0, 1082.0], [579.0, 1082.0], [579.0, 1265.0], [553.0, 1265.0]], [[525.0, 1084.0], [546.0, 1084.0], [546.0, 1257.0], [525.0, 1257.0]], [[490.0, 1081.0], [517.0, 1081.0], [517.0, 1243.0], [490.0, 1243.0]]], "lines": ["あんな普通の", "塾の授業なんて、", "おまえには退屈", "じゃないのか。"]}, {"box": [137, 1314, 291, 1493], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[267.0, 1317.0], [289.0, 1317.0], [289.0, 1417.0], [267.0, 1417.0]], [[232.0, 1315.0], [259.0, 1315.0], [259.0, 1493.0], [232.0, 1493.0]], [[201.0, 1315.0], [228.0, 1315.0], [228.0, 1443.0], [201.0, 1443.0]], [[170.0, 1315.0], [196.0, 1315.0], [196.0, 1475.0], [170.0, 1475.0]], [[137.0, 1314.0], [164.0, 1314.0], [164.0, 1456.0], [137.0, 1456.0]]], "lines": ["おまえは", "父さんが渡した", "問題集さえ", "やっていれば、", "それでいい。"]}], "img_path": "subarashii_sekai_02_006.jpg"}, {"v